%20a%20professional%20job.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThieves%20broke%20into%20a%20German%20bank%20vault%20over%20Christmas%20weekend%2C%20making%20off%20with%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20of%20valuables%20from%20over%203%2C000%20safe%20deposit%20boxes%2C%20say%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20definitely%20say%20this%20is%20quite%20spectacular%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Thomas%20Nowaczyk%2C%20a%20spokesman%20for%20the%20local%20police%2C%20in%20translated%20remarks.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20never%20heard%20of%20any%20similar%20case%2C%20except%20on%20TV.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Sparkasse%20Gelsenkirchen's%20branch%20in%20Buer%2C%20a%20suburb%20in%20western%20Germany%2C%20the%20holiday%20heist%20started%20with%20thieves%20breaking%20into%20a%20door%20and%20then%20drilling%20through%20the%20concrete%20bank%20vault%20wall.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20boxes'%20insured%20value%20was%20at%20least%2031%20million%20euros%2C%20or%20%2436%20million.%20The%20heist's%20full%20tally%20could%20be%20much%20higher%2C%20as%20some%20customers%20likely%20stored%20valuables%20exceeding%20the%20insurance%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20you%20must%20assume%20that%20your%20box%20has%20also%20been%20broken%20into%2C%26quot%3B%20Sparkasse%20Gelsenkirchen%20said%20on%20its%20website.%20%26quot%3BMore%20than%2095%25%20of%20the%20customer%20safe%20deposit%20boxes%20were%20forced%20upon%20by%20the%20as-yet-unknown%20perpetrators.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20spokesman%20said%20it%20was%20a%20professional%20job.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20hole%20that%20can%20now%20be%20seen%20also%20indicates%20that%20a%20very%20large%20special%20tool%20was%20used.%20Accordingly%2C%20it%20must%20have%20taken%20longer%20and%20was%20certainly%20not%20a%20spontaneous%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20Nowaczyk%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Associated%20Press%20reported%20that%20an%20early%20Monday%20fire%20alarm%20drew%20first%20responders%20to%20the%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Thieves%20drilled%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20concrete%20wall%20of%20a%20German%20bank%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6956069104eda4732f2e5a2a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThieves%20drilled%20this%20hole%20in%20the%20concrete%20wall%20of%20a%20German%20bank%2C%20say%20police.%3Cp%3EPolice%20Gelsenkirchen%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDozens%20of%20angry%20people%20gathered%20outside%20the%20branch%20early%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20fear%20my%20mother's%20gold%20coin%20is%20gone.%20She%20passed%20away%20in%201988.%20My%20grandmother's%20gold%20bracelets%2C%20which%20I%20hoped%20would%20secure%20my%20daughter's%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20woman%20told%20DW%20News%2C%20which%20translated%20her%20remarks%20to%20English.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Levi%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20criminology%20at%20Cardiff%20University%2C%20told%20DW%20News%20that%20banks%20often%20have%20less%20security%20vigilance%20during%20holiday%20weekends.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20thieves%20likely%20%26quot%3Bhad%20some%20level%20of%20inside%20information%26quot%3B%20to%20access%20the%20site%2C%20so%20investigators%20would%20look%20for%20dissatisfied%20employees%2C%20ex-employees%2C%20or%20contractors.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20large%20end%20of%20the%20scale%26quot%3B%20of%20robberies%2C%20Levi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthieves-germany-bank-vault-safe-deposit-sparkasse-gelsenkirchens-robbery-millions-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1767247440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F695608c2832e0ef1ead70bed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthieves-germany-bank-vault-safe-