0Capital's%20existing%20operations%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20comes%20as%20a%20proposal%20for%20a%20wealth%20tax%20was%20floated%20in%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiami's%20startup%20and%20finance%20scene%20heated%20up%20during%20the%20pandemic%20and%20in%20the%20years%20that%20followed%2C%20with%20many%20big%20firms%20from%20California%20and%20New%20York%20relocating%20their%20headquarters%20and%20expanding%20their%20offices%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESan%20Francisco-based%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFounders%20Fund%2C%20the%20venture%20capital%20firm%20cofounded%20by%20Thiel%2C%20has%20had%20an%20office%20in%20Miami%20since%202021.%20In%202020%2C%20Thiel%20bought%20an%20%2418%20million%20house%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-thiel-bought-miami-estate-featured-on-the-real-world-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMiami's%20Venetian%20Islands%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalifornia%20is%20debating%20a%20proposed%20wealth%20tax%20that%20would%20impose%20a%20one-time%205%25%20tax%20on%20residents%20with%20net%20worths%20exceeding%20%241%20billion%2C%20to%20be%20paid%20over%20five%20years.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wealth%20tax%20still%20needs%20870%2C000%20signatures%20to%20even%20make%20it%20to%20the%20ballot%20in%20November%202026%2C%20where%20it%20would%20then%20be%20approved%20or%20rejected%20by%20voters%20at%20the%20ballot%20box.%20However%2C%20billionaires%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehave%20already%20been%20critical%20of%20the%20plan%20and%20warned%20of%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-leaders-react-to-california-wealth-tax-proposal-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexodus%20of%20the%20wealthy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20proposed%20by%20SEIU-United%20Healthcare%20Workers%20West%20and%20designed%20to%20offset%20anticipated%20cuts%20to%20healthcare%2C%20education%2C%20and%20food%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frich-income-tax-capital-gains-ing-trust-nevada-delaware-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eincome%20tax%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20wealth%20tax%20is%20a%20levy%20on%20all%20of%20an%20individual's%20net%20worth%2C%20because%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20quantify%20the%20annual%20income%20of%20a%20person%20who%20doesn't%20earn%20normal%20paychecks%20but%20has%20other%20assets%20that%20gain%20value%20every%20year.%20The%20tax%20would%20apply%20to%20the%20roughly%20200%20billionaires%20residing%20in%20California%2C%20which%20has%20a%20total%20population%20of%20over%2039%20million%20people.%20The%20SEIU-UHW%20estimates%20that%20the%20one-time%20tax%20will%20bring%20in%20%24100%20billion%20over%20five%20years%20for%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECelebrity%20attorney%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falex-spiro-letter-gavin-newsom-stop-california-wealth-tax-billionaires-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAlex%20Spiro%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20Gov.%20Gavin%20Newsom%20on%20behalf%20of%20his%20clients%2C%20warning%20that%20his%20clients%20will%20%26quot%3Bpermanently%20relocate%26quot%3B%20if%20the%20California%20wealth%20tax%20passes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIzzy%20Gardon%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Newsom's%20office%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20governor%20has%20%26quot%3Bconsistently%20opposed%20state-level%20wealth%20taxes%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20a%20wealth%20tax%2C%20%26quot%3Bif%20implemented%20at%20a%20state-only%20level%2C%20they%20drive%20a%20race%20to%20the%20bottom.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20passed%2C%20the%20wealth%20tax%20would%20apply%20retroactively%20to%20all%20California%20residents%20as%20of%20January%201%2C%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-thiel-opens-office-miami-california-debates-billionaire-wealth-tax-2025-