2https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-microsoft-apple-h1b-visa-delay-warnings-memos-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%2C%20Apple%2C%20Microsoft%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20other%20companies%20to%20issue%20travel%20advisories%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20warning%20US%20employees%20with%20visas%20to%20avoid%20international%20travel%20to%20prevent%20extended%20stays%20outside%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20allows%20employees%20traveling%20abroad%20for%20visa%20renewals%20to%20work%20remotely%20for%20up%20to%2020%20business%20days%2C%20an%20exemption%20from%20the%20normal%20requirement%20that%20they%20work%20in%20their%20office%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-rto-policy-costing-it-top-tech-talent-ai-recruiters-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efive%20days%20%3C%2Fa%3Ea%20week.%20Now%2C%20any%20Amazon%20employee%20in%20India%20as%20of%20December%2013%20and%20who%20awaits%20a%20rescheduled%20visa%20appointment%20may%20work%20remotely%20until%20March%202%2C%20according%20to%20the%20memo%2C%20which%20was%20posted%20to%20Amazon's%20internal%20HR%20portal%20on%20December%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20permission%20to%20work%20remotely%20comes%20with%20a%20long%20list%20of%20constraints.%20Employees%20working%20remotely%20from%20India%20are%20barred%20from%20coding%20of%20any%20kind%2C%20including%20troubleshooting%20and%20testing.%20They%20cannot%20work%20from%20or%20visit%20Amazon%20buildings.%20And%20they%20cannot%20negotiate%20or%20sign%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20reviews%2C%20final%20decision%20making%2C%20and%20sign%20offs%20should%20be%20undertaken%20outside%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20memo%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memo%20also%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bin%20compliance%20with%20local%20laws%2C%20there%20are%20no%20exceptions%20to%20these%20restrictions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memo%20does%20not%20provide%20guidance%20for%20employees%20whose%20visa%20appointments%20have%20been%20rescheduled%20beyond%20March%202%2C%202026%2C%20or%20for%20those%20stranded%20in%20a%20different%20country.%20Some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-tells-visa-holders-stamp-leave-us-return-delays-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20embassies%20and%20consulates%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20rescheduled%20appointments%20as%20far%20out%20as%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20employees%20in%20technical%20roles%2C%20the%20restrictions%20raised%20questions%20about%20what%20work%20they%20can%20actually%20perform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeventy%20to%20eighty%20percent%20of%20my%20job%20is%20coding%2C%20testing%2C%20deploying%2C%20and%20documenting%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20Amazon%20software%20engineer%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20State%20Department%20spokesperson%20in%20December%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20social%20media%20reviews%20is%20to%20use%20%26quot%3Ball%20available%20tools%26quot%3B%20to%20flag%20visa%20applicants%20who%20are%20inadmissible%2C%20including%20those%20who%20pose%20a%20risk%20to%20national%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20delays%20pose%20a%20particular%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-salaries-engineers-analysts-ai-reshapes-tech-sector-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echallenge%20for%20Amazon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20among%20the%20largest%20users%20of%20the%20H-1B%20program.%20During%20the%202024%20government%20fiscal%20year%2C%20Amazon%20filed%2014%2C783%20certified%20H-1B%20applications%2C%20including%2023%20for%20Whole%20Foods%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F40-tech-companies-sponsor-most-h-1b-immigrant-workers-visas-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20publicly%20available%20data%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Labor%20and%20US%20Citizenship%20and%20Immigration%20Services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230df80dd-bde3-47b7-853f-6cac41a5efd0%5C%22%3ERead%20the%20full%20memo%20below%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EH-1B%2FH-4%20Visa%20Appointment%20Postponement%20Issue%20-%20December%2017%2C%202025%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Ch4%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2207e9ca29-67c0-452c-bba0-fb6a6ff5dea1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETemporary%20Remote%20Work%20Authorization%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Csection%3EEffective%20immediately%2C%20impacted%20employees%20who%20were%20in%20India%20as%20of%20December%2013%2C%202025%2C%20and%20are%20awaiting%20their%20rescheduled%20visa%20appointment%20may%20work%20remotely%20until%20March%202%2C%202026.%20You%20must%20follow%20all%20current%20limitations%20on%20remote%20work%20activities%2C%20including%20restrictions%20against%20coding.%20See%20the%20FAQs%20below%20for%20details.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWe%20continue%20to%20monitor%20developments%20closely%20and%20will%20provide%20further%20updates%20as%20more%20information%20becomes%20available.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20if%20you%20need%20additional%20support%20please%20reach%20out%20by%20asking%20Aza%20or%20contacting%20MyHR%20Live%20Support%20to%20be%20connected%20to%20an%20HR%20expert.%20You%20and%20your%20household%20also%20have%2024%2F7%20access%20to%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20support%20and%20resources%20through%20Resources%20for%20Living.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Ch4%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226ed44969-f0ef-4cf1-8380-684ab7c53781%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmployee%20Guidance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Csection%3EThe%20remote%20work%20grace%20period%20is%20subject%20to%20the%20same%20activity%20restrictions%20(listed%20below)%20as%20all%20current%20remote%20work%20guidance%20in%20India.%20In%20compliance%20with%20local%20laws%2C%20there%20are%20no%20exceptions%20to%20these%20restrictions.%20If%20you%20have%20questions%2C%20please%20work%20with%20your%20manager%20and%20HRBP%20to%20determine%20what%20activities%20you%20can%20engage%20in%20while%20abroad%2C%20based%20on%20these%20guidelines%3A%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDo%20not%20code.%20This%20includes%20troubleshooting%2C%20testing%2C%20or%20documentation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDo%20not%20work%20from%20or%20visit%20an%20Amazon%20building%20or%20site.%20All%20work%20must%20be%20remote%20from%20a%20residential%20address%20or%20other%20non-Amazon%20location.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDo%20not%20give%20the%20impression%20of%20authority%20to%20bind%20any%20Amazon%20entity%20or%20appoint%20an%20agent%20authorized%20to%20bind%20any%20Amazon%20entity%20to%20any%20contract%20or%20agreement.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDo%20not%20undertake%20any%20strategic%20business%20decisions%2C%20business%20planning%2C%20product%20management%2Fdevelopment%2C%20and%2For%20business%20development%20type%20activities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDo%20not%20negotiate%20any%20contracts%2C%20sign%2Fexecute%20or%20otherwise%20conclude%20any%20contracts%2C%20or%20secure%20any%20orders%2C%20either%20in%20the%20approval%20tools%20and%2For%20DocuSign%20(or%20via%20any%20other%20method).%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDo%20not%20render%20any%20services%20to%20any%20customer%20(resident%20or%20otherwise)%20or%20to%20any%20Amazon%20entity%20in%20the%20country%20where%20the%20employee%20is%20remotely%20working%2C%20or%20otherwise%20perform%20any%20activity%20that%20directly%20benefits%20an%20Amazon%20entity%20in%20the%20country%20where%20remote%20working%20is%20taking%20place.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDo%20not%20perform%20any%20activity%20relating%20to%20directing%2C%20controlling%2C%20or%20supervising%20or%20facilitating%20the%20day-to-day%20operations%20of%20any%20Amazon%20local%20entity%20or%20employee%20of%20an%20Amazon%20local%20team%20in%20the%20country%20where%20the%20employee%20is%20working%20remotely.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDo%20not%20make%20hiring%20decisions%20for%20any%20Amazon%20entities%20in%20India.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDo%20not%20perform%20any%20activity%20related