0the%20implications%20of%20the%20presentation%20in%20the%20Chinese%20capital%20are%20that%20these%20missiles%20will%20eventually%20be%20additions%20to%20China's%20already%20sizable%20land-based%20ICBM%20arsenal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-fielded-new-icbm-pentagon-report-says-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1767211544000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69555125832e0ef1ead70364%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-fielded-new-icbm-pentagon-report-says-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20DF-27%2C%20a%20conventional%20strike%20missile%20believed%20to%20be%20able%20to%20target%20ships%2C%20has%20an%20estimated%20range%20that%20reaches%20parts%20of%20the%20continental%20US.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cpanella%40businessinsider.com%20(Chris%20Panella)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-fielded-new-icbm-pentagon-report-says-2025-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Sleeping%20driver%20stopped%20on%20Will%20Rogers%20Turnpike%20%E2%80%94%20How%20a%20trooper%20stopped%20vehicle%20before%20a%20crash%20on%20an%20Oklahoma%20turnpike%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1767211489000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-126278707%2Cimgsize-16192.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwatch-sleeping-driver-stopped-on-will-rogers-turnpike-how-a-trooper-stopped-vehicle-before-a-crash-on-an-oklahoma-turnpike%2Farticleshow%2F126278684.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F126278684.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%20trooper%20on%20the%20Will%20Rogers%20Tu