0levels%20and%20suction%20power%20for%20specific%20rooms).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S7%20Stretch%20Ultra%20cleans%20up%20to%20a%20centimeter%20along%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20vacuum%20head%20and%20half%20a%20centimeter%20along%20the%20front%20edge.%20Dual%20scrapers%20prevent%20hair%20from%20tangling%20around%20the%20brushroll%20and%20wring%20out%20dirty%20water%2C%20while%20the%20brushroll%20is%20consistently%20cleaned%20with%20fresh%20water%2C%20to%20prevent%20streaks%20and%20re-depositing%20dirt%20so%20you're%20not%20spreading%20messes%20around%20your%20floor.%20The%20battery%20lasted%2032%20minutes%20during%20testing%2C%20and%20I%20only%20needed%20to%20refill%20the%20clean%20water%20tank%20at%20the%2020-minute%20mark%20and%20empty%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank%20at%2028%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20debris%20catcher%20in%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank%20requires%20reaching%20in%20to%20pull%20out%20accumulated%20dirt%2C%20but%20at%20least%20the%20S7%20Stretch%20Ultra%20uses%20185%20degrees%20of%20hot%20water%20and%20185%20degrees%20of%20hot%20air%20to%20fully%20clean%20and%20dry%20the%20brushroll%20in%20five%20minutes.%20The%20%24650%20price%20tag%20may%20be%20high%20for%20some%2C%20but%20this%20investment%20is%20well%20worth%20it%20if%20you%20have%20a%20midsize%20home%20and%2For%20pets%20or%20kids%20and%20want%20to%20thoroughly%20clean%20spills%20and%20pick%20up%20hard-to-see%20messes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e53dbdd-c647-4cd9-8034-12891171d619%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%5C%22%3ETineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tineco%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%20features%20a%203.6-inch%20LCD%20screen%20that%20displays%20both%20the%20iLoop%20smart%20sensor%20and%20a%203D%20cartoon%2C%20guiding%20users%20through%20the%20setup%20process%20and%20providing%20insights%20into%20maintenance%2C%20self-cleaning%2C%20and%20cleaning%20modes.%20Newer%20Tineco%20wet-dry%20vacuums%2C%20like%20the%20S7%20Stretch%20Ultra%2C%20have%20considerably%20smaller%20screens%2C%20so%20the%20S7%20Pro%20is%20a%20good%20fit%20for%20those%20with%20vision%20accessibility%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20clean%20water%20tank%20is%20on%20the%20vacuum%20body%2C%20so%20while%20you%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20make%20this%20vacuum%20lie%20180%20degrees%20flat%2C%20it%20can%20easily%20clean%20under%20low%20toe%20kicks%20and%20is%20outfitted%20with%20headlights%20to%20see%20debris%20in%20dark%20spaces.%20Performance-wise%2C%20it%20required%20three%20passes%20on%20dried%20ketchup%2C%20two%20passes%20on%20syrup%2C%20and%20a%20single%20pass%20on%20all%20other%20materials.%20Max%20or%20ultra%20modes%20are%20good%20for%20sticky%20messes%2C%20while%20suction%20mode%20is%20ideal%20for%20wet%20spills.%20In%20terms%20of%20edge%20support%2C%20you%20can%20clean%20within%20one%20centimeter%20along%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20vacuum%20head%20and%20within%203%2F4ths%20of%20an%20inch%20along%20the%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20by%20side%20of%20the%20tineco%20floor%20one%20s7%20pro%20cleaning%20coffee%20and%20in%20place%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca50656e2e190e71a38f54%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Floor%20One%20S7%20Pro%20has%20a%20large%20LCD%20screen%20that%20guides%20you%20through%20cleaning%2C%20and%20has%20headlights%20to%20make%20seeing%20the%20path%20in%20front%20of%20you%20easier.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20battery%20life%20of%20the%20S7%20Pro%20is%20advertised%20as%2040%20minutes%2C%20but%20I%20was%20able%20to%20use%20it%20for%2043%20minutes.%20There%20are%20two%20self-cleaning%20options%20%E2%80%94%20a%20two-minute%20self-cleaning%20and%20a%20super%20self-cleaning%20that%20lasts%206%20minutes.%20Neither%20use%20hot%20water%2C%20but%20they%20clean%20the%20brushroll%20thoroughly%20enough.%20Dust%20and%20