ney%20off%20these%20properties%20and%20more%20about%20spending%20time%20in%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228c5b27a9-18e6-4d04-bdf2-7a147f837fe3%5C%22%3EWe're%20exploring%20more%20of%20Japan%2C%20and%20there%20are%20still%20more%20business%20opportunities%20for%20us%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStockermans%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20would%20say%20mission%20accomplished%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20we're%20spending%20a%20lot%20more%20time%20in%20Japan%20than%20I%20thought%20we%20would%2C%20and%20it's%20getting%20more%20interesting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKurosawa%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It's%20been%20such%20a%20fun%20journey%20building%20this%20business.%20I%20think%20as%20we%20look%20at%20these%20new%20properties%2C%20we'll%20start%20exploring%20areas%20in%20Japan%20that%20none%20of%20my%20friends%20in%20Japan%20have%20ever%20been.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20men%20posing%20in%20a%20Japanese%20city.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F694c330b832e0ef1ead6cc36%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKurosawa%20and%20Stockermans%20in%20Japan.%3Cp%3EAkiyaMart%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKurosawa%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We're%20starting%20to%20help%20bridge%20Japanese%20connections%20with%20foreigners.%20I%20think%20the%20deeper%20we%20dive%20into%20the%20tech%20game%2C%20we%20quickly%20realized%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20Japanese%20websites%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20Japanese%20realtors%20%E2%80%94%20have%20no%20idea%20how%20to%20interact%20with%20foreigners.%20And%20also%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20owners%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20sell%20to%20foreigners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20people%20are%20now%20coming%20to%20us%20to%20be%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20we%20need%20your%20help.%20We%20want%20to%20sell%20to%20foreigners%20because%20locals%20aren't%20going%20to%20buy%20this%20property.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%