%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20farmers%20were%20not%20only%20able%20to%20enhance%20their%20income%20through%20premium%20pricing%20but%20also%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20addressing%20widespread%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F342444%2Fias-officer-avi-prasad-community-programme-to-fight-malnutrition-katni-madhya-pradesh-donate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eissues%20of%20malnutrition%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20developed%20through%20crossbreeding%20for%20nutritional%20benefits%20and%20climate%20resilience%2C%20showed%20promising%20results%20in%20increasing%20essential%20nutrient%20levels%20by%20up%20to%2080%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20introducing%20zinc%20soil%20bacteria%20to%20enrich%20the%20soil%20ecosystem%2C%20the%20seeds%20enabled%20plants%20to%20absorb%20more%20nutrients%2C%20ultimately%20leading%20to%20significantly%20higher%20nutritional%20content%20in%20the%20harvested%20crops%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22By%20encouraging%20the%20shift%20from%20traditional%20seeds%20to%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20farmers%20enhanced%20their%20income%20as%20well.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-768x402.jpg%20